trans-unit.source: Provides a mechanism whereby types can declare that they can receive an expression (or another class) from a markup extension, where the output is a different property type than the target property.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en mekanisme der typer kan deklarere at de kan motta et uttrykk (eller en annen klasse) fra filtypen markup der resultatet er en annen egenskapstype enn target-egenskap.

trans-unit.source: Do not use for [!INCLUDE[net_v40_short](~/add/includes/net-v40-short-md.md)] implementations; see Remarks.
trans-unit.target: Ikke bruk for [!INCLUDE[net_v40_short](~/add/includes/net-v40-short-md.md)] implementeringer; se kommentarer.

trans-unit.source: In [!INCLUDE[net_v30_short](~/add/includes/net-v30-short-md.md)], IReceiveMarkupExtension was a WPF-specific technique for permitting types to enter a different codepath whenever any of its XAML-accessible members where set as markup extensions during XAML parsing.
trans-unit.target: I [!INCLUDE[net_v30_short](~/add/includes/net-v30-short-md.md)], IReceiveMarkupExtension er en WPF-spesifikke fremgangsmåte for å gi typer til å angi en annen codepath når eventuelle XAML tilgjengelig medlemmer der angitt som markup utvidelser under XAML analyse.

trans-unit.source: In [!INCLUDE[net_v40_short](~/add/includes/net-v40-short-md.md)], this interface is obsolete, and is replaced with a .NET Framework XAML Services implementation for how markup extensions can receive services or types can invoke markup-extension specific setter logic.
trans-unit.target: I [!INCLUDE[net_v40_short](~/add/includes/net-v40-short-md.md)], typer kan aktivere markup filutvidelsen bestemte setter logic dette grensesnittet er foreldet og erstattes med en .NET Framework XAML Services implementering for hvordan markup utvidelser kan motta tjenester eller.

trans-unit.source: For [!INCLUDE[net_v40_long](~/add/includes/net-v40-long-md.md)] implementations, if types want to perform special processing when setting properties by markup extension rather than by other means, types should be defined with <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XamlSetMarkupExtensionAttribute> attributes applied.
trans-unit.target: For [!INCLUDE[net_v40_long](~/add/includes/net-v40-long-md.md)] implementeringer, hvis typer vil utføre spesielle behandling når du angir egenskapene ved markup filtypen i stedet for på andre måter typer må defineres med <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XamlSetMarkupExtensionAttribute>attributter som brukes.</xref:System.Windows.Markup.XamlSetMarkupExtensionAttribute>

trans-unit.source: The attribute specifies a callback, which is typically defined as a private member of the type.
trans-unit.target: Attributtet angir et tilbakekall som vanligvis er definert som en privat medlem av typen.

trans-unit.source: In infrastructure implementations of WPF classes, most cases where <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XamlSetMarkupExtensionAttribute> is applied reference a `ReceiveMarkupExtension` method that previously implemented this interface, but now instead use context through the callback.
trans-unit.target: I infrastrukturen implementeringer av WPF klasser, de fleste tilfeller hvor <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XamlSetMarkupExtensionAttribute>er brukt referanse en `ReceiveMarkupExtension` metode som tidligere implementert dette grensesnittet, men nå i stedet bruke konteksten via tilbakeringing.</xref:System.Windows.Markup.XamlSetMarkupExtensionAttribute>

trans-unit.source: Provides the handling for markup extensions that provide property values.
trans-unit.target: Gir behandling for markup utvidelser som gir egenskapsverdier.

trans-unit.source: Do not use for [!INCLUDE[net_v40_short](~/add/includes/net-v40-short-md.md)] implementations; see Remarks in <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.IReceiveMarkupExtension"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Ikke bruk for [!INCLUDE[net_v40_short](~/add/includes/net-v40-short-md.md)] implementeringer; se merknader i <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.IReceiveMarkupExtension"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The name of the target property.
The markup extension instance of the incoming data.
Can provide additional services that should be performed when processing the markup extension data for a property value.
trans-unit.target: Kan gi andre tjenester som skal utføres under behandling av markup utvidelsen dataene for en egenskapsverdi.
